    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It's in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom! I've babied this car since day one, and it really shows in every little detail. If you're looking for a ride that's basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
