      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This S54-powered coupe features a high-pressure double VANOS system and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. Comprehensive preventative maintenance has been performed, including a VAC Motorsports rod bearing service and a TMS subframe reinforcement kit to ensure chassis rigidity. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with the factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal power delivery. The exterior retains its factory depth with no signs of oxidation, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or pixel degradation. A mechanically synchronized, turn-key example for the purist.",
